ygData.messageBody:
Hello all,
I am just wondering, what is the best place to gain levels at lvl 17 soloing. I keep getting bashed by sandgiants in oasis and want to find a safe, not very crowded spot to gain leves at. Also What are the stats on the Ghoulsbane Dmg/del ratio etc. Also what about other holy swords. Also had anyone heard of when the two other continents are coming up? and what changes will that make to the gameing system, will there be more spells, access to lvls higher than lvl 50 etc.
Thank you
Laurana Highwind
Paladin of Tunare, 17th rank
The Rathe
List Moderator
